@catchability TangaroaMatureq
type nuisance
lower_bound 0.01
upper_bound 1.50

@catchability TangaroaImmatureq
type nuisance
lower_bound 0.01
upper_bound 1.50

@observation TangaroaAcousticMature
type biomass
time_step step2
time_step_proportion 0.5
categories male.spawn+female.spawn
selectivities One One
catchability TangaroaMatureq
likelihood lognormal
process_error 0.1
years 1993 1994 1995 1998 2000 2002 2004 2006 2009 2011 2013 2016 2019 2022
table obs
1993 16060 0.24
1994 72168 0.34
