2019 91145 0.27
2022 91968 0.20
end_table

@observation TangaroaAcousticImmature
type biomass
time_step step2
time_step_proportion 0.5
categories male.nonspawn+female.nonspawn
selectivities TangaroaImmatureSel TangaroaImmatureSel
catchability TangaroaImmatureq
likelihood lognormal
process_error 0.1
years 1993 1994 1995 1998 2000 2002 2004 2006 2009 2011 2013 2016 2019 2022
